Struct Mapped

Source 
#[repr(transparent)]
pub struct Mapped<B, D>
where
    B: BytesMapping<D>,
{
    _mapping: PhantomData<(B, D)>,
    repr: B::Bytes,
}
Expand description

A container for the bytestring that is produced from BytesMapping conversion

Fields
